Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.05,0:00:08.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(330,400)\fad(1000,000)}聖天空戰記
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.43,0:00:12.43,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是只要墜入愛河每個人都會變得如此孤單?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.51,0:00:21.42,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是正擁抱著比黑暗要更深沉的苦楚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.48,0:00:34.56,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一切必定都是為了讓我倆能綻放光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.03,0:00:39.47,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我愛著你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.53,0:00:43.97,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直用心凝視著你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.04,0:00:48.48,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信著你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.54,0:00:53.04,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便是在寒冷的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.07,0:01:15.50,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在用淚水來呼喚你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.57,0:01:20.03,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不需要約定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.11,0:01:28.91,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你早就給了我 最寶貴的堅強
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.43,0:00:12.43,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ねえ 愛したら誰もが こんな孤独になるの
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.51,0:00:21.42,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ねえ 暗闇よりも深い苦しみ 抱きしめてるの
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.48,0:00:34.56,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何もかもが二人 輝くためきっと
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.03,0:00:39.47,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君を君を愛してる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.53,0:00:43.97,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心で見つめている
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.04,0:00:48.48,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君を君を信じてる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.54,0:00:53.04,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寒い夜も
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.07,0:01:15.50,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涙で今呼びかける
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.57,0:01:20.03,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約束などいらない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.11,0:01:28.91,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君がくれた大切な強さだから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.42,0:01:34.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是夢?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.99,0:01:36.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是我的幻覺?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.83,0:01:41.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻擊法尼利亞的巨人\N讓亞連的守城也陷入了一片火海
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.90,0:01:46.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯,我的預感再度成真了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.60,0:01:49.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巨人從空中攻擊我們
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.34,0:01:53.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙讓艾斯嘉科尼化身為龍
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.78,0:01:56.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了讓我們逃走,獨自一人離開
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.71,0:01:58.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將巨人們引開…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.01,0:02:03.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂,你不快點逃的話,可是會被我追上的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.76,0:02:11.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧,我快要擊中你了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.21,0:02:25.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風向亂了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.96,0:02:44.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.83,0:02:48.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又隱形了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.94,0:03:00.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.68,0:03:04.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.75,0:03:13.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被我逮到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.36,0:03:18.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是自願當餌好讓其他人脫逃,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.23,0:03:22.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最討厭這種愛耍帥的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.24,0:03:35.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭的不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.02,0:03:43.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼快就不行了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.39,0:03:45.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是想殺死他嗎?迪蘭度
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.12,0:03:47.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你應該是要捉活他的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.42,0:03:52.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是跟他玩玩罷了,軍師大人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.10,0:04:03.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兄弟的刻印
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.91,0:04:14.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有火,看到火光了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.52,0:04:16.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有看到裝甲的殘骸嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.38,0:04:17.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒看到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.72,0:04:18.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.49,0:04:20.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道,梵大人他…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.22,0:04:23.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不,他們不會殺梵的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.43,0:04:28.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽說只有法尼利亞王\N才能夠敔動艾斯嘉科尼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.56,0:04:29.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.63,0:04:31.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們一定會去救他的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.17,0:04:34.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想還他這筆人情債
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.80,0:04:36.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這□氣我吞不下去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.70,0:04:37.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.07,0:04:38.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要宰了他們
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.87,0:04:41.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長,你打算怎麼做?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.61,0:04:42.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還剩下多少人?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.11,0:04:44.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連我在內一共有7名士兵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.91,0:04:49.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要對付那座浮游要塞正面攻擊可能有點吃力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.79,0:04:53.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之,得先掌握他們的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.62,0:04:58.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…亞連
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.39,0:05:03.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…我可能有辦法知道梵現在人在哪裏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.40,0:05:08.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的守城會遭到攻擊的事的確被你說中了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.84,0:05:09.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.77,0:05:12.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那並不是什麼巧合
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.14,0:05:13.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以感覺到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.94,0:05:18.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從小預感就蠻準的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.81,0:05:22.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…其實我自己也不懂是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.28,0:05:24.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是,我的那股能力越來越強了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.92,0:05:27.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算真是那樣好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.76,0:05:30.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這終究是我們騎士的職責所在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.29,0:05:31.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能諒解吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.80,0:05:38.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就請你測試一下我的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.80,0:05:39.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.69,0:06:04.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經派了討伐隊過去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.46,0:06:07.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些傢伙是回不了國的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.83,0:06:11.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也不需要繼續在這裏躲躲藏藏的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.07,0:06:13.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能太過大意
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.30,0:06:16.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先等他們的回報吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.00,0:06:18.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你總是那麼小心翼翼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.52,0:06:30.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過,這下子我們的未來就能高枕無憂了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.82,0:06:34.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點將裏頭的武士拖出來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.19,0:06:35.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後把它破壞掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.29,0:06:37.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能讓你這麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.16,0:06:38.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.23,0:06:41.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得等到我查明
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.76,0:06:44.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它為什麼會危害到我們的未來才行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.94,0:06:53.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我找出原因之前…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.00,0:07:15.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這傢伙是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.63,0:07:21.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對,他就是新任的法尼利亞王
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.35,0:07:37.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嚇得我渾身冒冷汗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.73,0:07:57.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個小妞真的能知道老大的過去嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.57,0:07:58.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噓
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.01,0:07:59.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安靜點
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.54,0:08:02.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,IL Pazzo,愚者的卡片
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.01,0:08:05.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自我中心的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.88,0:08:07.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無視於常理的行動
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.32,0:08:11.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你父親的個性就展現在這張卡片上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.75,0:08:16.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那道陰影覆蓋了你的家人導致關係崩潰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.79,0:08:18.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家人的分離
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.83,0:08:20.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂,她說對了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.50,0:08:21.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天曉得
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.80,0:08:24.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為老大不喜歡說他的過去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.13,0:08:26.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被我說中了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.00,0:08:31.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的妹妹之所以會失蹤還有母親的病逝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.31,0:08:32.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都是因為他父親…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.14,0:08:34.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.61,0:08:36.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.01,0:08:38.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他好像在生氣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.98,0:08:40.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不是說了不該說的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.85,0:08:48.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過,我一定要取得亞連的信任才行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.99,0:08:50.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳,你怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.09,0:08:51.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.53,0:08:53.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管了,說就說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.70,0:08:57.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,IL Giudizio,審判的卡片
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.07,0:08:59.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不久的將來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.73,0:09:02.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有機會和你的父親重逢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.60,0:09:07.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你執著於過去無法將心中的仇恨給…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.14,0:09:10.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.31,0:09:13.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這張卡片是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.42,0:09:16.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.82,0:09:17.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.79,0:09:21.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.79,0:09:23.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你及格了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.06,0:09:28.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快把梵的所在地找出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.40,0:09:30.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.89,0:09:54.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是誰?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.46,0:10:02.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會唱法尼利亞的民謠?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.28,0:10:17.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶我去拿我的人型裝甲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.88,0:10:23.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以為這種恐嚇就能讓寨巴哈士兵屈服嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.69,0:10:27.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是無法離開這座浮游要塞的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.79,0:10:35.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與其要成為你們的道具茍活下去,還不如…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.04,0:10:45.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以浪費生命
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.35,0:10:57.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王兄?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.64,0:11:16.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣子真的會有辦法知道嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.24,0:11:22.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總會有辦法的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.11,0:11:28.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不見了,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.98,0:11:30.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有十年了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.22,0:11:33.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直都相信著
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.82,0:11:36.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王兄並不是逃避了繼承王位的儀式
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.26,0:11:38.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是與龍戰鬥而死的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.86,0:11:43.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從未背朝敵人奮戰至最後一刻才犧牲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.60,0:11:47.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是為什麼你會在寨巴哈?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.00,0:11:49.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要將法尼利亞燒成廢墟?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.01,0:11:53.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答我,王兄
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.04,0:11:56.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼好笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.31,0:12:00.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別再笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.55,0:12:03.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.42,0:12:09.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟我一起去見寨巴哈皇帝多倫卡喀大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.09,0:12:13.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後一同目睹嶄新的未來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.55,0:12:39.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.95,0:12:42.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用,請讓我繼續
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.79,0:12:45.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是…要是有什麼他接觸過的東西就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.43,0:12:47.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.80,0:12:48.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.70,0:12:53.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我該怎麼做才好?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.30,0:12:57.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,專心地…想著他
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.39,0:13:23.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏是"漂流大地"的聚集地
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.40,0:13:25.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漂流大地?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.20,0:13:26.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.43,0:13:29.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意思就是跟這艘船一樣是漂浮的岩石
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.40,0:13:33.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對喔,那裏是那個浮游要塞的最佳藏匿處
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.48,0:13:37.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.68,0:13:38.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作點
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.45,0:13:44.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙就是會威脅到寨巴哈帝國未來的東西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.19,0:13:47.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過是個古董罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.12,0:13:50.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過,弗肯那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.33,0:13:54.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會有辦法操縱它呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.51,0:14:05.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.51,0:14:06.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它在那裏
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.61,0:14:09.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發現浮游要塞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.54,0:14:10.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.41,0:14:11.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加熱浮游石
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.98,0:14:14.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解除浮力,一□氣攻入要塞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.59,0:14:21.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浮力減少至20
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.12,0:14:22.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.96,0:14:23.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收帆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.06,0:14:24.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,降落
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.39,0:14:58.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.59,0:15:00.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停機庫發生原因不明的爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.83,0:15:02.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵軍來襲,就在正上方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.53,0:15:03.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.84,0:15:08.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下錨
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.81,0:15:16.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浮力恢復
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.91,0:15:18.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好,鬆開鎖鏈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.48,0:15:19.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收起推進器
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.79,0:15:28.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後方系留船錨發射
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.70,0:15:37.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好,登陸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.07,0:15:38.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.07,0:15:40.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突擊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.51,0:15:47.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.88,0:15:50.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.08,0:15:52.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.35,0:15:53.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.72,0:15:58.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟發生了什麼事?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.43,0:16:11.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寶藏…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.37,0:16:13.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪蘭度大人呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.47,0:16:13.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不曉得
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.47,0:16:15.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若沒有迪蘭度大人的指示
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.10,0:16:16.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不能行動
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.40,0:16:18.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家快分頭去找
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.61,0:16:19.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.41,0:16:26.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾斯嘉科尼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.05,0:16:27.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可疑人物
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.52,0:16:33.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好,你可別亂動喔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.73,0:16:38.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞連
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.50,0:16:47.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.53,0:16:48.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.84,0:16:49.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.87,0:16:50.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得過去才行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.01,0:16:51.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去哪裏?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.94,0:16:53.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得去通知梵才行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.51,0:16:54.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你等等啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.02,0:17:02.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來你平安無事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.35,0:17:04.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞連
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.35,0:17:05.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是來救我的嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.95,0:17:07.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒時間了,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.56,0:17:15.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距離5公尺
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.20,0:17:17.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不,應該有6公尺
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.20,0:17:24.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.87,0:17:25.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.01,0:17:30.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你究竟想要做什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.58,0:17:32.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫我拿著
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.41,0:17:35.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要跳過去那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.12,0:17:35.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.68,0:17:39.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的跳遠紀錄是5公尺40
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.49,0:17:41.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.96,0:17:44.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底在想什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.36,0:17:46.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能跳得過去的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.39,0:17:47.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相隔那麼遠耶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.96,0:17:49.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掉下去的話會死的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.60,0:17:51.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會摔爛的耶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.40,0:17:52.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你聽我說…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.70,0:17:53.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.96,0:18:19.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.20,0:18:26.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪…怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.40,0:18:30.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快,我得快點去通知他
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.26,0:18:49.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾斯嘉科尼就在前面
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.89,0:18:50.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏交給我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.16,0:18:51.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.90,0:18:56.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.23,0:18:57.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.61,0:19:05.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王兄
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.28,0:19:08.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王兄?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.61,0:19:10.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵的?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.58,0:19:18.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王兄
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.79,0:19:19.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.86,0:19:28.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵,後面
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.13,0:19:36.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時候我早該宰了你的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.70,0:19:39.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我討厭你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.47,0:19:41.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.61,0:19:42.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭的不得了!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.22,0:19:59.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的臉…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.46,0:20:00.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳,走這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.66,0:20:01.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的臉…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.60,0:20:02.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.33,0:20:08.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞連,撒退吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.37,0:20:10.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迦迪斯,準備撒退
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.10,0:20:11.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.14,0:20:17.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兄弟們,作戰結束
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.08,0:20:17.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.76,0:20:30.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你竟然…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.06,0:20:34.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你竟然將我這張俊美的臉…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.77,0:20:43.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯多利亞高速船起飛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.34,0:20:43.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.14,0:20:45.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能源石能量…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.14,0:20:45.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法恢復
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.04,0:20:47.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機械輸出動力為零
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.38,0:20:49.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.74,0:20:52.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你遲早會來到我的身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.58,0:20:55.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵大人!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.22,0:20:59.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.29,0:21:01.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.99,0:21:04.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本來是想救你們的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.23,0:21:07.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果反倒是你們救了我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.96,0:21:09.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這全都是托她的福
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.90,0:21:10.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.27,0:21:14.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.54,0:21:16.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.94,0:21:18.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右滿舵
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.01,0:21:21.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到阿斯多利亞的都城"帕拉斯"去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.18,0:21:23.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帕拉斯…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.53,0:22:55.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞連
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.20,0:22:57.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜拉娜公主
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.74,0:23:04.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在找確嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.38,0:23:07.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謀略之都
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.80,0:21:57.87,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月兒彼方藍色探照燈照耀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.41,0:22:06.32,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然降臨的天使 你究竟是誰?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.78,0:22:13.95,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命運的門扉即將開啟　So just fall in love
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.26,0:22:20.10,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕不放過這令人興奮的瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.17,0:22:22.46,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't stop,baby
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.70,0:22:27.47,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那燃燒般的神秘雙眸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.54,0:22:31.31,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天真無邪的笑容讓我傾倒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.38,0:22:35.11,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞳眸深處的暗示只傳遞給你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.18,0:22:39.12,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始了無止盡的旅程
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.18,0:22:42.62,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內心的鼓動無法抑制
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.68,0:22:50.09,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想帶著你一起走
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.80,0:21:57.86,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月の向こう　蒼い Search light　重なる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.41,0:22:06.31,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然舞い降りたAngel　そう　君は誰?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.78,0:22:13.95,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今　運命の　扉が開く　So just fall in love
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.26,0:22:20.09,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸騒ぎするこの瞬間を逃がさない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.16,0:22:22.46,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't stop,baby
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.70,0:22:27.47,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,焼けそうな　君の Mystic eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.54,0:22:31.30,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無邪気な笑顔で　Breaking down
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.37,0:22:35.10,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君だけに　瞳の奥の合図
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.18,0:22:39.11,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果てない　旅は始まる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.18,0:22:42.62,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,もう止まらない　胸の鼓動
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.68,0:22:50.09,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君を　さらっていきたい

